d.andP;  The PN48 includes a lightweight(1/2 pound) rechargeable NiCAD battery pack and lists for $549.andM;For more information contact Citizen America, U.S.andP;  headquarters are locatedat 2450 Broadway, Suite 600, Santa Monica, Calif., 90404-3060; Phone:213/453-0614.andM;(Linda Rohrbough/19910520/Press Contact: Bob Adams, Citizen,Tel:213/453-0614, Fax:213/453-2814)</TEXT></DOC>